criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Willing and able to consent to participate (written, informed consent);

          -  Willing and able to attend/complete the requested follow-up visits;

          -  Considered for treatment for Neuropathy with SALVATION™ External Fixation, SALVATION™
             Fusion Bolts and Beams, SALVATION™ Midfoot Nail, The SALVATION™ 3Di Plating System,
             and/or VALOR™ NAIL

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects determined, by the investigator, to be an inappropriate candidate for the
             procedure indicated;

          -  Unable to consent to participate (written, informed consent);

          -  Unable to attend/complete the requested follow-up visits
